fields.description:
Update inbuilt Git to 2.5.0

{quote}
Git 2.5.1
Release Notes (2015-08-28)
{quote}

If proxy is enabled on Sourcetree, diff preview does not load for Java files, diff preview will be stuck at loading.

When trying to run {{git diff}} on the files via command line from the terminal, it will fail with this error message:

{noformat}fatal: unable to read files to diff{noformat}

When I use "restart merge" in a file configured to use eol=crlf in .gitattributes. Source Tree converts all end of line in this file to LF.

Steps to reproduce this bug:
#         Use the attached repository;
#         Do a merge between branches master and Test;
#         Note that the end of line in the "test.txt" file is as CRLF;
#         Use Restart Merge in file "test.txt";
#         Note that the end of line in the "test.txt" file is as LF;

I opened a request in Atlassian Support https://support.atlassian.com/servicedesk/customer/portal/1/STSP-2329 but I think this is the correct place.
